    K'Nex Mario Vs Goombas Building Set

    • Ref:  042331
    Previous Next
    • Zoom
    • Description
    • Reviews
    • Delivery & Returns
    Bring Mario Kart to life with the Knex Mario Vs Goombas Building Set! Build Mario in his Kart and race past the Goombas! The set includes the parts to build Mario, a Standard Kart with battery-powered motor, a Goomba obstacle and 2 collectible items from the game! Also includes 6 pieces of buildable track.
